# Out-of-tree build of the open BCM4916 XRDP Runner CPU-conduit datapath driver
# plus the Phase-1 L2/VLAN HW flow-offload layer.
#
# The module is composed of three objects; the composite is named
# bcm4916-runner (dash) so it does not collide with the bcm4916_runner.o
# component object. Produces bcm4916-runner.ko.
obj-m += bcm4916-runner.o
bcm4916-runner-y := bcm4916_runner.o cmdlist.o flow_offload.o
